Haxe mode for Emacs:

* https://bitbucket.org/jpsecher/haxe-mode - from Jens Peter Secher (not maintained anymore; see https://bitbucket.org/jpsecher/haxe-mode/issues/2/haxe-mode-does-not-indent)
* http://lists.motion-twin.com/pipermail/haxe/attachments/20090430/2feee92b/haxe-mode.obj - from David Bergman
* https://github.com/pierre-arlaud/funda-haxe-mode - from Pierre Arlaud

Haxe completion:

* https://github.com/cloudshift/hx-emacs [seems a bit flaky, may need some tweaking --AmitPatel]
* https://groups.google.com/forum/#!topic/haxelang/9Z-j1B2qgsg - discussion and partial code
* http://www.dafishinsea.com/blog/2010/01/21/getting-ctags-to-work-with-actionscript-and-haxe/ - ctags and haxe
